{"tid":254004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【柯潔戰AlphaGo】10年後AI盛世 兩個打工仔有一個要轉行","createTime":"2017-05-22T23:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T17:49:01.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b48f94c371e9485daac68c4d578162b46381571","tid":254004,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T23:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170522/large/1495452610_6bf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170522%2Flarge%2F1495452610_6bf3.jpg&h=3cef25ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在科技界，人工智能（AI）超越人類智慧的一刻被稱為「奇點」，對人類社會的衝擊類似宇宙誕生大爆炸時的「奇點」。隨AI技術不斷發展，這個「奇點」已經越來越逼近。曾在蘋果、Google、微軟擔任高層的李開復在上世紀80年代取得人工智能博士學位，他在最近公開表示，10年內AI或令50%人類工作崗位被取代。<br />\n<br />\n李開復指，預計人工智能在DNA檢測，藥物試驗，發明新材料等範疇將得到廣泛應用。但AI在傳統行業更有優勢，其中最大的應用是在無人駕駛，世界上10%的人的工作都跟駕駛有關。另外，在圖像識別、語音識別方面，機器的識別率已超越人的識別率，這意味那些主要靠「聽」和「看」吃飯的人要被機器取代。比如「看臉」作為核心工作的保安；比如那些靠「聽」吃飯的人，包括客服、翻譯等。10年之後，世界上90%的工作，也許50%的人類崗位可能都要面臨被取代。<br />\n<br />\nAI則已一早殺入金融界，大量交易員已被交易程式取代。高盛在紐約總部的股票交易櫃枱曾有600名交易員，現時只剩2人。有業界分析指，日後大量行業分析師、宏觀經濟分析師等主要依靠數據的崗位，也極有可能被取代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728220&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728220%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=nC8wVHy36zhM20HqL3oKBF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b6e1f84d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728220%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=616a341d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728220&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"1b5d7fda5fd3dadbdf66b99cbb8e47047e29b8b1","tid":254004,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T23:39:39.000Z","msg":"到時會有新產業同新職位"},{"pid":"01b65e1aeda5a21489793e7712280ab0abea14f2","tid":254004,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:33:15.000Z","msg":"到時可以搵份幫人工智能更換電池的工作"},{"pid":"2cd858379bede228de67465364f8c918ca31b683","tid":254004,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"我肯定到時design都係要人手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7779137d46a466ee03d83648bc9d32bf1724961","tid":254004,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我肯定到時design都係要人手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時咪一堆人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8ee8097c6b79a453bad5e871bec3ee022cb21","tid":254004,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:40:20.000Z","msg":"人類文明要消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdb5c57430049188b348ed59f286da7e43bbf75","tid":254004,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類文明要消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n超人類卓比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eeede5d30763566f73aafa352f4144e713ef6e","tid":254004,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"快點取代我<br />\n<br />\n利申 IT狗"},{"pid":"3b63b56ba1d8afa1a8ccfaba8110b4d11251a0cd","tid":254004,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我肯定到時design都係要人手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時咪一堆人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他行業少左人